0 -16 Td
(Design goals:) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Keep operational state obvious: running, stopped, error, authenticated, last update, and command actions should scan quickly.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Preserve developer trust with native system typography, code-friendly contrast, visible borders, and restrained motion.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Use compact density for dashboards and sidebars, but keep controls at least 44px high when touch use is plausible.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Prefer semantic tokens over one-off values so generated reports, OpenCode UI surfaces, and dashboard screens stay consistent.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Colors) Tj
0 -16 Td
(The canonical palette is derived from the dashboard CSS in .opencode/server/mcp-dashboard.ts:) Tj
0 -16 Td
